<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= naslov %></title>
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <link rel='stylesheet' href='/stylesheets/style.css' />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.2.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-sm bg-light fixed-top">
        <div class="container-fluid">
          <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="mynavbar">
            <div>
              <a href="/"><img src="images/logo.png" style="width: 50%"></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="d-flex" id="mynavbar">
            <ul class="navbar-nav px-3">
              <li class="nav-item px-2">
                <a class="nav-link" href="login" style="text-decoration-line: underline;">Login</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item d-flex">
                <a href="registracija">
                  <button class="btn dugmici">Registruj se</button>
                </a>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </nav>
    </div>
    <br>
    <div class="container-fluid py-5 forma-publika text-center">
        <div class="row py-3">
          <h3 class="">Pridružujete se kao publika?</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="row mx-5 px-5">
          <form action="/predavanje/pitanja" method="post">
            <div class="input-group px-5" style="border-radius: 30px">
                <input type="text" class="form-control" placeholder="# Unesite kod" aria-label="# Unesite kod" aria-describedby="basic-addon2" name="kod" id="kod" style="border-radius: 30px">
                <span class="input-group-btn">
                  <button class="btn kod-dugmic" type="submit" style="border-radius: 30px">
                    <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="16" height="16" fill="currentColor" class="bi bi-arrow-right" viewBox="0 0 16 16">
                      <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M1 8a.5.5 0 0 1 .5-.5h11.793l-3.147-3.146a.5.5 0 0 1 .708-.708l4 4a.5.5 0 0 1 0 .708l-4 4a.5.5 0 0 1-.708-.708L13.293 8.5H1.5A.5.5 0 0 1 1 8z"/>
                    </svg>
                  </button>
                </span>
            </div>
          </form>
        </div>
      <% if(messages.kod_nije_validan) { %>
        <div class="row mx-5 my-1">
          <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
            <%= messages.kod_nije_validan %>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% } %>
    </div>

    <div class="container mt-3">
      <div class="mt-4 p-5 text-grey rounded">
        <h1>Interakcijska aplikacija za hibridni način predavanja</h1>
        <p>Uključite vašu publiku u predavanje - bilo da je sastanak u uredu, online ili hibridno.</p>
        <p>Ova aplikacija Vam nudi sve što Vam je potrebno da angažujete Vaše sudionike i da se svi osjećaju povezano
          - bilo da predajete na zajedničkom pozivu, predavanju ili sastanku cijele firme.</p>
        <p>Publika se može pridružiti bez prijave ili preuzimanja aplikacije, i setup za
          predavače zahtijeva samo par minuta</p>
        <a href="/registracija">
          <button class="btn btn-success">Započnite besplatno</button>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
      <footer class="my-2">
        <ul class="nav justify-content-center border-bottom pb-3 mb-3">
        </ul>
        <p class="text-center text-muted">© 2023 Projekat Slido</p>
      </footer>
    </div>

    <br>
  </body>
</html>
